A temporary work-around (if you want a file on the server) would be: import streamlit as st import os
def file_selector(folder_path='.'): filenames = os.listdir(folder_path) selected_filename = st.selectbox('Select a file', filenames) return os.path.join(folder_path, selected_filename)
filename = file_selector() st.write('You selected `%s`' % filename) Please see <denchmark-link:https://discuss.streamlit.io/t/upload-files-to-streamlit-app/80/2>this topic</denchmark-link> for more ideas!
